column1: #motor - motor of the scooter used (in kW)
#latitude_points - latitude of the points where must pass (<Latitude>!<Latitude>!...)
#longitude_points - longitude of the points where must pass (<Longitude>!<Longitude>!...)
#elevation - percentage of elevation (can be possitive or negative) - (<Elevation>!<Elevation>!...)
#current_bat of the scooter used (in percentage, ex: 45, 23...)
#charge - if it can charge or not(y/n)
